videos.description: After Evan Boudreaux knocks down a 3-pointer, Jahaad Proctor steals the ball and scores a layup to give Purdue a 42-21 lead over Iowa.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Purdue pours it on with 2 quick buckets) 2020/03/03

videos.headline: Purdue pours it on with 2 quick buckets

videos.description: With the shot clock winding down, Purdue's Eric Hunter Jr. knocks down a 3-pointer with two Iowa defenders in his face.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Hunter's contested 3 beats shot clock for Purdue) 2020/03/03

videos.headline: Hunter's contested 3 beats shot clock for Purdue
